  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This version extends the project period, according to ECHO&#xB4;s extension and adjusts FY09 budget.  Project belongs to P00377. Its main objective is to strengthen local capacities in disaster risk reduction and preparedness in urban neighbourhoods and rural communities affected by natural hazards due to the &#x2018;El Ni&#xF1;o&apos; phenomenon in the Piura river basin, linking the activities and lessons learnt at sub -national, national and Andean -regional levels.</narrative>
